STEPS TO USING PRETTIER


1. Make a prettier config file
	https://prettier.io/docs/en/configuration.html
2. save that file as .prettierrc in root
	this file is ignored via github  .. example below
3. on command line run ..
	bundle exec rbprettier --write '**/*.rb'
4. done





.prettierrc


{
  "tabWidth": 4,
  "semi": false
}